snippet.title: BEACHHEAD 2020 | Introduction
snippet.description:
BEACHHEAD 2020 - it's not just a game, it's the future of reality

20 years ago, BEACH HEAD 2000 changed the gaming paradigm by bringing a new gaming experience to life. 20 years later, the original game creators are ready to do it again. 
WELCOME TO BH2020 and a new dimension in gaming.

Learn more:
Discord: https://discord.gg/7WRzXZEpK2
Website: https://beachhead2020.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/beachhead2020/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/beachhead2020
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/beachhead2020
